Provenance & clean-room statement
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

keephippo is an independent, clean-room implementation of a Vault-compatible
HTTP API. It is not affiliated with, endorsed by, or derived from the source
code of HashiCorp Vault (BUSL-1.1). It is implemented against the public HTTP
API specification, using the MPL-2.0 licensed OpenBao project
(https://openbao.org) as a reference where needed.

Any individual source file adapted from an MPL-2.0 work retains that file's
original MPL-2.0 header and copyright, per the license's file-level copyleft.
As of this scaffold, no such files have been adapted.

